snippet.title: NETHILI FISH FRY | White Anchovy Fish Recipe Cooking in Village | Crispy Fried Fish Recipes
snippet.description:
In this video, we prepare fresh Nethili fish (White Anchovy) using a traditional village-style frying method. The fish is marinated with a blend of aromatic spices and deep-fried over a wood fire, creating a crispy and flavorful dish.

What‚Äôs in this video:

Cleaning and marinating fresh Nethili fish with homemade spices.

Deep-frying in a large vessel over a traditional firewood setup.

A golden, crispy texture with an authentic village-style taste.

This cooking method enhances the fish's natural flavors while maintaining a perfect balance of crunch and spice. Nethili fish fry is a popular home and street food dish in South Indian coastal cuisine, known for its rich taste and crispy finish.

snippet.description:
Peri Peri Chicken Pola | Chicken Cake 

Ingredients :

FOR PERI PERI CHICKEN FRY
--------------------------------
chicken -1/2 kg
chilli powder  -1 tbsp
paprika powder  -1/2 tsp
Ginger garlic paste -2 tsp
lime juice -1 tbsp
vinegar -1 tbsp
oregano -1/4 tsp
Black pepper powder  -1/2 tsp
maida -1 tbsp
salt
oil -2-3 tbsp

FOR PERI PERI SAUCE
------------------------------------
onion -1/2 
garlic -3
dry red chillies -3
water -1/4 cup

FOR FILLING
-------------------
oil -1 tbsp
onion -2
red bell pepper -1/2
cumin seeds powder  -1/4 tsp
Black pepper powder  -1/4 tsp
salt
peri peri sauce
Prepared chicken 
coriander leaves

FOR BATTER
---------------------
eggs -3
milk -3/4 cup
salt
oil -1/4 cup
maida -1 cup
baking powder  -1/4 tsp

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.

snippet.title: Get Ready For An Action-Packed Season!
snippet.description:
Buckle up, soldier! The villainous Minion General is striking across the land like a Lightning Spell. There's only one fighting force strong enough to stop him: the Action Heroes!

Clash of Clans "Action Heroes" Season starts March 1st 08:00AM UTC! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

A new city, a shared space, and the same unspoken bond. As Amit and Darshana settle into their new routine in Pune, their friendship deepens‚Äîlate-night talks, quiet moments, and an unmissable closeness. But while Darshana sees a trusted companion, Amit feels something more. Will he find the courage to tell her what‚Äôs in his heart, or will his feelings remain‚Ä¶ saved in drafts?

snippet.title: Badshah - Dear Aditya (Official Music Video) | Hiten
snippet.description:
A Letter To Myself

Audio Credits :
‚ûü Performed By Badshah
‚ûü Lyrics By Badshah
‚ûü Composed By  Badshah
‚ûü Music Produced By Hiten 
‚ûü Mixed & Mastered By Hiten
‚ûü Chorus Performed by Vaidik Dawale, Aanya Jain, Veda Mahajan & Advik Kasbe

Lyrics: 
Kaisa hai kya haal hai kya chal raha hai
Gaane vaane sun raha hai ya padh raha hai
Jitna marzi rishtedar tere peeche padein dekh
Dariyo na tu sapne dekh aur bade dekh
Ye jaankar tu aaj bada dang hoga
Ke pandran saal mein in sabka mooh band hoga
Jin teacheron ko tujhse zaraa bhi ummeed nai thi un saare teacheron ki naak mein dum

Papa ka thoda dhyaan rakh unka dil kamzor hai
Tere aas paas aadhe se zaada bande chor hain
Dost kam rakhiyo circle usse chota
Paisa boht aane wala hai wallet mota rakhiyo
Maa baap ke siva koi saga nai milega
Sukoon ghar ko chod kisi jagah nai milega
Jisko pyaar tu karega dil wo tera todegi
Kisi paise wale ke liye wo tujhe chodegi
Ek dedh hafta rona, man kare to chillana
Lekin fir chup chaap wapas music pe lag jaana
Uski yaad mein koi sad songs nahi banaiyo
Log waise hi boht rote hain tu party karaiyo

Koi dedh chaal chale to tu dhai samajhna
Par jo pakde tera hath use bhai samajhna
Par kain baar hath deke hathon ki lakeerein le jaate hain log tab hathon ki safai samajhna
Hateron ka dil dekh dehelte rahega
Shuru jaise marzi karaa ant keher se karega
2 kamron ke ghar mein tha janma tu tujhe pata nahi tu ek din kitne bade mahal mein rahega
Maa khush hogi lekin papa khush ni rahenge
Unka man hai tu IAS bane par push ni karenge
Log teri lagataar kaamyaabi dekh bore hoke hate karenge par mooh pe kuch ni kahenge

Haan‚Ä¶. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan‚Ä¶. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Behkaave mein aake tu sidein switch nai karna
Fame ke chakkar mein kisiko diss nai karna
Khoob mehnat karna sirf wish nai karna
Aur jab saamne nishaana ho to miss nai karna
tujhe ladna hi hoga
Chahe kat jayen taangein aage badhna hi hog
Yaad rakh fame ek kiraaye ka makaan hai
Ek din tujhe ise khali karna hi hoga
jaam na sharaab lena, pyaar behisaab dena
Mooh kam kholiyo tu Kaam se jawaab dena
Banda tujhse kya chahe aankhon se bhaanp lena
Jo karega wo bharega khud ko na paap dena

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Haan‚Ä¶. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan‚Ä¶. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. ‚õèÔ∏è Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie ‚Äì only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie,‚Äù directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (‚ÄúWednesday‚Äù), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (‚ÄúThe Color Purple‚Äù), Sebastian Hansen (‚ÄúJust Mercy, ‚ÄúLisey‚Äôs Story‚Äù), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn‚Äôt just help you craft, it‚Äôs essential to one‚Äôs survival! Four misfits‚ÄîGarrett ‚ÄúThe Garbage Man‚Äù Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)‚Äîfind themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they‚Äôll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative‚Ä¶the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (‚ÄúNinety-Five Senses,‚Äù ‚ÄúNacho Libre‚Äù) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans √ìlafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director‚Äôs creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (‚Äú127 Hours,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), editor James Thomas (‚ÄúPok√©mon: Detective Pikachu‚Äù, the ‚ÄúBorat‚Äù films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), and costume designer Amanda Neale (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúWhat We Do in the Shadows‚Äù). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok,‚Äù the ‚ÄúLEGO¬Æ‚Äù movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie.‚Äù The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 3 | Flowers | EP # 230
